{
  "_description": "聚陽 M7 列管 ↔ 客戶 PDF 命名 alias 對照表。consolidate_canonical.py 後續 normalize 步驟用,把 medium confidence 的衝突降為 high。",
  "_updated": "2026-05-08",
  "_source": "Elly 業務知識 + canonical_consensus_report.txt 衝突清單反推",

  "客戶": {
    "_rule": "客戶全名 → 縮寫(M7 列管慣例 vs PDF 簡寫)",
    "DICKS SPORTING GOODS": "DKS",
